The [`Validate.col_count_match()`](`Validate.col_count_match`) validation method checks if the number of columns in a table
matches a specified count.

::: {#33072e08 .cell execution_count=24}
``` {.python .cell-code}
(
    pb.Validate(data=pb.load_dataset(dataset="small_table", tbl_type="polars"))
    .col_count_match(count=8)
    .interrogate()
)
